N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 396.5 - Definitions

State Regulations

For purposes of this Part: (a) Public assistance means family assistance
and safety net assistance or the former aid to dependent children or home
relief programs; and
(b) Office
means the Office of Temporary and Disability Assistance. Notes
